<p style="text-align:center; color:black;font-family:'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif">
    The automotive market offers a diverse range of vehicles tailored to various needs and preferences. For instance,
    the Toyota Camry and Honda Accord are popular sedans known for their reliability, fuel efficiency, and advanced
    safety features, making them ideal for family use. On the other hand, the Ford F-150 and Chevrolet Silverado 1500
    dominate the pickup segment, boasting impressive towing capacities and rugged performance, perfect for those needing
    a workhorse. In the SUV category, models like the Honda CR-V and Toyota RAV4 stand out for their spacious interiors
    and versatility, appealing to adventure seekers and families alike. For environmentally conscious drivers, the Tesla
    Model 3 offers an electric option with cutting-edge technology and long-range capabilities. Meanwhile, the Mazda CX-5
    combines sporty handling with a premium interior, while the Subaru Outback provides rugged durability and all-wheel drive
    for outdoor enthusiasts. Lastly, the Nissan Altima balances comfort and performance, making it a solid choice in the sedan
    market. Each of these vehicles brings unique attributes to the table, catering to different lifestyles and driving preferences.</p>
